w-3xl\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap items-end justify-between gap-4\"><div><p class=\"text-[11px] font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-faint\">Street Team</p><h1 class=\"mt-1 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\">The people carrying your film</h1></div><button class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap rounded-lg text-sm font-medium transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-1 focus-visible:ring-foreground/40 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 bg-foreground text-background hover:bg-foreground/90 h-10 px-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-user-plus h-4 w-4\"><path d=\"M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2\"></path><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"7\" r=\"4\"></circle><line x1=\"19\" x2=\"19\" y1=\"8\" y2=\"14\"></line><line x1=\"22\" x2=\"16\" y1=\"11\" y2=\"11\"></line></svg> Invite</button></div><div class=\"rounded-xl border border-border bg-surface mt-8 p-0\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-[1fr_auto_auto] items-center gap-x-6 px-6 py-3 text-[11px] font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-faint\"><span>Member</span><span>Status</span><span class=\"text-right\">Contribution</span></div><div class=\"divide-y divide-border border-t border-border\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-[1fr_auto_auto] items-center gap-x-6 px-6 py-4\"><div class=\"min-w-0\"><p class=\"truncate text-sm font-medium\">Anjali Menon K</p><p class=\"text-[13px] text-faint\">Street Team Lead</p></div><span class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full border px-2.5 py-0.5 text-[11px] font-medium tracking-wide border-emerald-900 text-emerald-400\">Active</span><p class=\"text-right text-sm tabular-nums text-muted\">1240 pts</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-[1fr_auto_auto] items-center gap-x-6 px-6 py-4\"><div class=\"min-w-0\"><p class=\"truncate text-sm font-medium\">Rahul Varma</p><p class=\"text-[13px] text-faint\">Fan Community</p></div><span class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full border px-2.5 py-0.5 text-[11px] font-medium tracking-wide border-emerald-900 text-emerald-400\">Active</span><p class=\"text-right text-sm tabular-nums text-muted\">980 pts</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-[1fr_auto_auto] items-center gap-x-6 px-6 py-4\"><div class=\"min-w-0\"><p class=\"truncate text-sm font-medium\">Sneha Pillai</p><p class=\"text-[13px] text-faint\">Campus Ambassador</p></div><span class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full border px-2.5 py-0.5 text-[11px] font-medium tracking-wide border-emerald-900 text-emerald-400\">Active</span><p class=\"text-right text-sm tabular-nums text-muted\">760 pts</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-[1fr_auto_auto] items-center gap-x-6 px-6 py-4\"><div class=\"min-w-0\"><p class=\"truncate text-sm font-medium\">Arun T S</p><p class=\"text-[13px] text-faint\">Theatre Network</p></div><span class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full border px-2.5 py-0.5 text-[11px] font-medium tracking-wide border-amber-900 text-amber-400\">Invited</span><p class=\"text-right text-sm tabular-nums text-muted\">—</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-[1fr_auto_auto] items-center gap-x-6 px-6 py-4\"><div class=\"min-w-0\"><p class=\"truncate text-sm font-medium\">Divya Nair</p><p class=\"text-[13px] text-faint\">Meme Unit</p></div><span class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full border px-2.5 py-0.5 text-[11px] font-medium tracking-wide border-emerald-900 text-emerald-400\">Active</span><p class=\"text-right text-sm tabular-nums text-muted\">1510 pts</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-[1fr_auto_auto] items-center gap-x-6 px-6 py-4\"><div class=\"min-w-0\"><p class=\"truncate text-sm font-medium\">Jose Kurian</p><p class=\"text-[13px] text-faint\">Regional Press</p></div><span class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full border px-2.5 py-0.5 text-[11px] font-medium tracking-wide border-border text-muted\">Paused</span><p class=\"text-right text-sm tabular-nums text-muted\">420 pts</p></div></div></div></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main><aside class=\"hidden w-80 shrink-0 border-l border-border px-6 py-8 xl:block\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-[13px] font-medium text-muted\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-sparkles h-4 w-4\"><path d=\"M9.937 15.5A2 2 0 0 0 8.5 14.063l-6.135-1.582a.5.5 0 0 1 0-.962L8.5 9.936A2 2 0 0 0 9.937 8.5l1.582-6.135a.5.5 0 0 1 .963 0L14.063 8.5A2 2 0 0 0 15.5 9.937l6.135 1.581a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .964L15.5 14.063a2 2 0 0 0-1.437 1.437l-1.582 6.135a.5.5 0 0 1-.963 0z\"></path><path d=\"M20 3v4\"></path><path d=\"M22 5h-4\"></path><path d=\"M4 17v2\"></path><path d=\"M5 18H3\"></path></svg>Campaign Brain</div><section class=\"mt-6\"><p class=\"text-[11px] font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-faint\">Today&#x27;s recommendation</p><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed\">Lock the main trailer this week. Teaser momentum peaks around day 10 — releasing the trailer inside that window compounds reach instead of restarting it.</p></section><section class=\"mt-6 rounded-xl border border-border bg-surface p-4\"><p class=\"text-[11px] font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-faint\">Next action</p><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed\">Approve trailer cut two, then schedule the drop for Friday 6pm with a street-team push in the first hour.</p><p class=\"mt-3 inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[13px] font-medium\">Do it now <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-3.5 w-3.5\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></p></section><section class=\"mt-6\"><p class=\"text-[11px] font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-faint\">Campaign summary</p><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted\">Thira is in the Trailer phase, 33 days from release. Health is 78 and trending up: press coverage is ahead of plan, but the music phase has no confirmed dates yet — that is the biggest open risk.</p><p class=\"mt-4 text-xs text-faint\">Thira<!-- --> · <!-- -->122<!-- --> days to release</p></section></aside></div><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-5974c4836639bfc7.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[5175,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n3:I[5115,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n4:I[7414,[\\\"873\\\",\\\"static/chunks/873-2e3382f29d22c519.js\\\",\\\"598\\\",\\\"static/chunks/598-8df30065fdf4105c.js\\\",\\\"944\\\",\\\"static/chunks/app/(app)/layout-da3311b6db55d021.js\\\"],\\\"AppShell\\\"]\\n5:I[1618,[],\\\"ClientPageRoot\\\"]\\n6:I[5120,[\\\"873\\\",\\\"static/chunks/873-2e3382f29d22c519.js\\\",\\\"593\\\",\\\"static/chunks/app/(app)/team/page-20f191684520e7ba.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n9:I[6478,[],\\\"OutletBoundary\\\"]\\nb:I[51,[],\\\"AsyncMetadataOutlet\\\"]\\nd:I[6478,[],\\\"ViewportBoundary\\\"]\\nf:I[6478,[],\\\"MetadataBoundary\\\"]\\n10:\\\"$Sreact.suspense\\\"\\n12:I[973,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n:HL[\\\"/_next/static/css/16f691357524a009.css\\\",\\\"style\\\"]\\n\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"0:{\\\"P\\\":null,\\\"b\\\":\\\"O8XQVddIoYPthci-mAKUA\\\",\\\"p\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"c\\\":[\\\"\\\",\\\"team\\\"],\\\"i\\\":false,\\\"f\\\":[[[\\\"\\\",{\\\"children\\\":[\\\"(app)\\\",{\\\"children\\\":[\\\"team\\\",{\\\"children\\\":[\\\"__PAGE__\\\",{}]}]}]},\\\"$undefined\\\",\\\"$undefined\\\",true],[\\\"\\\",[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$1\\\",\\\"c\\\",{\\\"children\\\":[[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"link\\\",\\\"0\\\",{\\\"rel\\\":\\\"stylesheet\\\",\\\"href\\\":\\\"/_next/static/css/16f69135